Class PicoInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.picotech.picoscope.PicoInfo

  • public final class PicoInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    PicoInfo contains a set of constants used to define PICO_INFO constants listed in the PicoStatus.h file.
